application

Class Parttime

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Employee
      • application.Parttime

  • public class Parttime
extends Employee
    This class is for the Part-time type employee which retains characteristics of the superclass Employee but also with unique characteristics of a part time employee. Unique characteristics of this class are the payRate and hours parameters as these employees are paid hourly unlike Full-time and Management employees. The methods used for this class are toString(), equals(), getHours(), inputHours(), getPayRate(), and calculatePayment().
    Author:
    Jasmin Kaur, Jonathan Delin
